nodes.text: A male Human Padawan served the Jedi Order and the Galactic Republic during the Mandalorian Wars.

A Force-sensitive Human was trained in the ways of the Force by the Jedi Order during the Mandalorian Wars, attaining the rank of Padawan. Following the appointment of Jedi Master Lucien Draay to the Jedi High Council he was assigned to assist in moving Draay's belongings into his new apartment within the High Council Tower on Coruscant. Along with another Padawan, they completed the assignment as Draay arrived to take up residence.
